Module lab3OrinyakKI306

Class Sea

java.lang.Object
lab3OrinyakKI306.WaterBody
lab3OrinyakKI306.Sea
public class Sea extends WaterBody
The Sea class represents a body of water in the program, extending the WaterBody class and implementing the Volume interface. It encapsulates information about the salinity and depth of the sea.
